{"tid":751860,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"人誰無過？粉絲們聯署簽名希望迪士尼重新接受 James Gunn","createTime":"2018-07-22T09:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T01:53:04.000Z","uid":41343,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c131884d0bebfd45c168281845ed13173bc0ca1c","tid":751860,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:02:49.000Z","msg":"在昨日的突發消息表示，《Guardians of the Galaxy》導演 James Gunn 因多年前的不雅言論遭到 Disney 解僱。消息傳出後隨即引起各界震驚，畢竟 James Gunn 的玩笑是十年前發生，如今卻被人重新找出來，引起一片譁然及批評也是無可奈何。但是總會有人認為 James Gunn 的玩笑罪不致死，始終人誰無過呢？因此一位 James Gunn 支持者 Chandler Edwards 便發起請願，希望迪士尼重新接受 James Gunn，請願現在已獲得超過 30,000 個的簽名支持。同時在 Twitter 上亦有不少網民都對這次事件發表意見，希望迪士尼重新考慮一番，更連不少參與 Marvel 電影的演員如 Dave Bautista、David Destmalchian、Patton Oswalt 也在社交媒體上為 James Gunn 作辯護。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/marvel-re-hire-james-gunn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fmarvel-re-hire-james-gunn&d=jM4Xazfkj6lOjvklLJQOxb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=61d8d122\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/marvel-re-hire-james-gunn</a>"},{"pid":"94035d12dfb28fa568897ec78d7e0afd0a85e381","tid":751860,"uid":167426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:07:14.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361fff8047038fda8ffd0f1761104298be5c27ad","tid":751860,"uid":195428,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為佢拍嘅電影好睇所以有戀童傾向都可以無視？"},{"pid":"f5944c414293adda49eb0cbc56442d148888d8e4","tid":751860,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"361fff8047038fda8ffd0f1761104298be5c27ad","tid":751860,"uid":195428,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為佢拍嘅電影好睇所以有戀童傾向都可以無視？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T10:28:06.000Z"